Former vice president, Atiku Abubakar, is currently at the Nigerian Senate. The Peoples Democratic Party (PDP) candidate at the 2019 presidential election is appearing as one of the stakeholders at a public hearing. The hearing is on a bill for the conversion of the the Modibbo Adama University of Technology to a conventional university The public hearing is being held at room Room 231 of the Senate conference area. Details later… Download Daily Post App.    Subscribe to Daily Post Newsletter.    Advertise with us.   Send us enquiries, press releases.